terrified kid.

13:31.900 --> 13:36.500
And I'm afraid what's going
through his head right now,

13:36.500 --> 13:38.800
sitting alone in that hell hole.

13:38.800 --> 13:40.667
- What would you
like to happen?

13:40.667 --> 13:44.033
