to help you with that.

14:17.000 --> 14:18.700
- How?

14:18.700 --> 14:22.066
- I'm gonna
read to you.

14:22.066 --> 14:27.200
"The Adventures of Tom Sawyer,"
chapter one.

14:27.200 --> 14:30.934
